{"id": "art-2030", "label": "Art. 2030", "title": "Art. 2030: Modurile de încetare", "slug": "art-2030", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1529940693\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1055\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1529940693\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 2030:\nModurile de încetare </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_837982622\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1054\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_837982622\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Pe lâng&#259;\ncauzele generale de încetare a contractelor, mandatul înceteaz&#259; prin\noricare dintre urm&#259;toarele moduri:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_183611871\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1053\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_183611871\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)revocarea sa de c&#259;tre mandant;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1969224237\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1052\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1969224237\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)renun&#355;area mandatarului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1388015395\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1051\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1388015395\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)moartea, incapacitatea sau falimentul mandantului ori a\nmandatarului. Cu toate acestea, atunci când are ca obiect încheierea unor acte\nsuccesive în cadrul unei activit&#259;&#355;i cu caracter de continuitate,\nmandatul nu înceteaz&#259; dac&#259; aceast&#259; activitate este în curs de\ndesf&#259;&#351;urare, cu respectarea dreptului de revocare sau renun&#355;are\nal p&#259;r&#355;ilor ori al mo&#351;tenitorilor acestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_688695243\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1050\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_688695243\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul mandatului de ocrotire, orice persoan&#259;\ndintre cele prev&#259;zute la art. 111 poate, dac&#259; mandatul nu este\nexecutat corespunz&#259;tor, s&#259; solicite instan&#355;ei de tutel&#259;\ns&#259; dispun&#259; revocarea acestuia, îndeplinirea obliga&#355;iei\nmandatarului de a da socoteal&#259;, precum &#351;i o m&#259;sur&#259; de\nocrotire cu privire la mandant.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1304215360\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1049\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1304215360\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Mandatul de ocrotire cu titlu gratuit nu înceteaz&#259;\nprin falimentul mandantului.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}